node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ROAM THE PLANET in Norway with @karolnienartowicz. May be an image of nature, mountain and lake.

node.text:

Photo by @karolnienartowicz

Share your story: #roamtheplanet

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ROAM THE PLANET in Croatia with @harrypope. May be an image of nature and body of water.

node.text:
This 150m deep river spring located in the South of Croatia makes for a nice way to cool off from the summer heat! ☀️ In fact you only need to dip your toes to realise how cold the water is!
Photo by @harrypope
Share your story: #roamtheplanet
